description:
Comment: [v1] 58 pages, 14 figures, published in the Astronomical Journal;
  [v2] Title and minor typos corrected to match published version, and
  references updated

  In this paper we show positive mass theorems and Penrose type inequalities
for the Gauss-Bonnet-Chern mass, which was introduced recently in \cite{GWW},
for asymptotically flat CF manifolds and its rigidity.
